This would be more correct, perhaps:
```javascript
var to_date = to_picker.datepickerdata.date();
from_picker.datepickerdata.maxDate(to_date ? to_date : false);
var from_date = from_picker.datepickerdata.date();
to_picker.datepickerdata.minDate(from_date ? from_date : false);
